<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<title>Halaman tidak ditemukan!</title>

	<link href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" id="bootstrap-css">
	<style>
		body { background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,);}
		.error-template {padding: 40px 15px;text-align: center;}
		.error-actions {margin-top:15px;margin-bottom:15px;}
		.error-actions .btn { margin-right:10px; }
		h1{
			font-size: 250px;
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="error-template">
                <h1>
                    404
				</h1>
                <h2>
                    Halaman tidak ditemukan!</h2>
                <div class="error-details">
					Maaf, halaman yang anda akses tidak ditemukan, Halaman yang anda akses kemungkinan telah dihapus.
                </div>
                <div class="error-actions">
                    <a href="/" class="btn btn-default btn"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-home"></span>
                        Halaman Utama
					</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<script src="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script src="//code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.1.min.js"></script>	
</body>


</html>
